# All the features discussed over multiple teams meetings <br/>
<br />

# Feature: Registration/Login - 90% Aryan Khetani 10% Manraj Singh
## This feature helps user to login with the care giver or care taker profile

# Feature: Magnification - Devarshi Vyas 50% Manraj Singh 50%
## This feature is used to magnify objects in realtime using camera view and flash.

# Feature: Image Transcription - Devarshi Vyas 60% Manraj Singh 40%
## This Task help in converting camera captured or gallery image into text which is further used in Media Player feature

# Feature: Media Player - Leah Isenor 100%
## This feature converts the text data received from image Transcription feature to

# Feature: Implement Database - Leah Isenor 100%
## This part is used to connect to the firebase and store and retrieve files

# Documentation Gallery - Zifan 100%
# This feature lists all the documents as per their categories

